Package com.group52.bank.transaction

Class TransactionSystem

java.lang.Object
com.group52.bank.transaction.TransactionSystem
public class TransactionSystem extends Object
This class represents a Transaction System in the banking application. It manages transactions, their history, and unchecked transactions.
